# Project: Speech Analyzer App (Buildathon Practice)

## Overview
This is a Next.js 14 App Router application that records a user's voice, 
transcribes it using ElevenLabs Speech-to-Text API, and then provides 
AI-powered feedback through 3 different analysis cards.

## Tech Stack
- Framework: Next.js 14 (App Router, NOT Pages Router)
- Language: TypeScript
- Styling: Tailwind CSS
- Speech-to-Text: ElevenLabs Scribe API
- AI Feedback: Anthropic Claude API (claude-sonnet-4-20250514)
- Deployment: Vercel

## Code Rules
- Always use the App Router (app/ directory), never pages/
- Use TypeScript for all files
- Use Tailwind CSS for all styling — no CSS files unless absolutely necessary
- Keep API keys in .env.local, access them only in server-side API routes
- API routes go in app/api/ folder
- Use async/await — no .then() chains
- Always handle loading states and error states in the UI

## Project Structure
app/
  page.tsx          ← Main UI page (the recorder + 3 cards)
  api/
    analyze/
      route.ts      ← Server-side: calls ElevenLabs STT + Claude AI

## ElevenLabs Speech-to-Text
- Endpoint: POST https://api.elevenlabs.io/v1/speech-to-text
- Header: xi-api-key: process.env.ELEVENLABS_API_KEY
- Body: FormData with fields: model_id="scribe_v1" and file=(audio blob)
- Returns JSON with a "text" field containing the transcript

## Anthropic Claude
- Use the official @anthropic-ai/sdk package
- Model: claude-sonnet-4-20250514
- Call it 3 times in parallel (Promise.all) with different system prompts
  for the 3 analysis cards

## The 3 Analysis Cards
1. COUNTER: Count filler words (um, uh, like, you know, basically, literally, 
   actually, right, okay, so) — give exact counts per word and total
2. GRAMMARIAN: Analyze grammar, sentence structure, vocabulary richness. 
   Point out specific errors with corrections.
3. EVALUATOR: Overall speech quality — clarity, confidence, structure, pacing, 
   content. Give a score out of 10 and actionable tips.

## UI Requirements
- Dark theme preferred
- "Start Speaking" button that turns red when recording
- Show recording timer while recording
- Show loading spinners on cards while AI is thinking
- Cards appear with a nice animation when results arrive
- Mobile-friendly layout